			<description><![CDATA[<p>
	We have full time and part time Lead Specialist positions available. If you would like an opportunity to work with a company that cares about their associates, we have a position for you.<br />
	We are currently the fastest growing and most successful business lead marketing firm in the US. We integrate cutting-edge lead extraction technology with advanced marketing systems.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p>
	<strong>Job Description</strong><br />
	As a Lead Specialist, no matter if your background is in sales, customer service, retail, accounting, management or anything else you will have the opportunity to use your entrepreneurial spirit. You will be in constant contact with small business owners, real estate agents and contractors.<br />
	Because there are no territory restrictions, you can build your business around your schedule and be in control of your own destiny. Our training and support program is one of the strongest in the industry and will equip you to be a successful Lead Specialist. As a Lead Specialist, you make very good upfront income as well as have ongoing residual income as your customer base grows.</p>
<p>
	<strong>Job Responsibilities</strong><br />
	Our Lead Specialists have the opportunity to be in business for themselves, but not by themselves. We strongly support your sales and marketing efforts to help you become successful. Here is what we expect from our Lead Specialist:<br />
	As a Lead Specialist, your primary focus will be to sell business leads and software technology-based solutions daily to contractors, real estate agents and business owners in your town/city<br />
	Specific job duties will involve communicating the benefits of using our business leads and software<br />
	Networking and building your value proposition as you work your sales territory<br />
	Maintaining a strong relationship with you customers to insure great customer service and continue your stream of residual income<br />
	Managing your sales activities and scheduling</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;<strong>Requirements </strong><br />
	Customer Service, sales and management experience we find are the most successful, but we are willing to train the right associates to be successful with our service. But you must have strong communication skills along with the ability to build solid working relationships with a variety of businesses. Applicants must possess an interest in learning new technology in an evolving industry, the ability to work autonomously and excellent time management skills.<br />
	Desire to have unlimited income and no sales territory restrictions<br />
	Strong networking and relationship building skills, as much of your business will come through referrals.&nbsp;<br />
	Integrity and strong work ethic<br />
	Good customer service and math skills<br />
	Experience with excel, word and the internet.<br />
	&nbsp;</p>
<p>
	&nbsp;<strong>Benefits</strong><br />
	We value our team and strive to provide one of the best business opportunities in the country. We are committed to our people having an opportunity that fits their schedule and lifestyle. Here are some of the benefits you can expect from working with us as an outside sales representative in the credit processing business:<br />
	Superior ongoing training programs that equip you with everything you need to be successful<br />
	Professional marketing and presentation materials<br />
	24/7 technical and customer support<br />
	One of the strongest commission plans in the industry. Guaranteed<br />
	Strong bonus payment plans<br />
	Fast payment of commissions through direct deposit<br />
	Residual income opportunities as you build your customer base<br />
	<br />
	&nbsp;</p>
]]></description>
